description:
&lt;p&gt;An exciting opportunity has arisen with the COVID-19 Clinical Assessment Service (CCAS). We are looking for HR &amp; Training Support Assistants to support CCAS. These posts will support the service up until 31March 2021.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are proud to say that CCAS has already on-boarded over 2,000 GPs and Clinicians. As the second wave of COVID-19 is emerging we need to increase the CCAS capacity and have therefore re-opened our portal for further GP recruitment. These roles will help us to on-board additional GPs and also provide ongoing support and management of the current workforce.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The postholder will ensure a high level HR and Training support service is provided. This includes support with ID checks, completion of statutory/mandatory training, off-boarding and general queries, and administration tasks.&lt;/p&gt;
